PREREQUISITES
=====================================================================

Debian packages:

*) package perl-modules
*) libdate-calc-perl
*) libcurses-ui-perl
*) texlive-latex-extra
*) texlive-lang-german

todo

USAGE
=====================================================================

./papabank jimknopf

replace jimknopf by any account name, for which you have created
an according subdirectory of 'accounts'.

so far not internationalised but hardcoded in German language

